name: Metaphys Daedalus
desc: If this card is Special Summoned by the effect of a "Metaphys" monster: You can banish all other face-up Special Summoned monsters on the field. Once per turn, during the Standby Phase, if this card was banished last turn: You can shuffle this banished card into the Deck; banish 1 "Metaphys" card from your Deck, except "Metaphys Daedalus" or "Metaphysical Regeneration".
